"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"金色财经报道，Block（前身为Square）旗下支付应用程序Cash App现在将允许美国用户将[比特币](https://www.bitcoin86.com/)和传统股票作为礼物发送给其他Cash App美国用户。虽然Stockpile和Coinbase等服务分别允许用户赠送股票和[加密货币](https://www.bitcoin86.com/)，但Cash App指出，这是点对点支付应用程序中首次提供此类功能。新的“赠送”功能使用户可以使用他们的CashApp美元余额或借记卡发送比特币，而不仅仅是现有的比特币余额。这意味着用户无需在CashApp应用程序上实际拥有任何比特币或股票，即可将其作为礼物发送。\",\"timestamp\":1639817533,\"title\":\"Cash App允许用户将比特币作为礼物发送给其他美国用户\"},\"digest\":\"8qcrSBP_Ozgy1JiK9tveh3b6iOc4rzjOFZ7HpVnkRTc\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xaA7CEF7E6482d885734088F912bD97832799e716\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"aIJtMz7DaAmNsI06GbrBdKj4mJzJoW_HWs_gQJnWaZ8\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"CBUa2FRUuZM1LVZBfhqLhcYNVWwWaJN3ZREt42f8Vh8\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"FZB28pDM4i3DBWJnhoXzHgERILSn8G71SvFDcM-retowJptd3p1iL9lD95g-4NIv7sxiaWQAZ_rO79qqHpJYnw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xab83893a494877da0bca08755c14f53124dae5665c20c6e1e378c738d0e6fa675fc7aa386da42c0bc2bf7f678f40f6669bdfeeada49902cfc7bada2bd95985161b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"aIJtMz7DaAmNsI06GbrBdKj4mJzJoW_HWs_gQJnWaZ8\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"CBUa2FRUuZM1LVZBfhqLhcYNVWwWaJN3ZREt42f8Vh8\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"8qcrSBP_Ozgy1JiK9tveh3b6iOc4rzjOFZ7HpVnkRTc\"}"